channel.title: Adding teleports to TrisidiaV3's custom teleport interface
channel.description: I am new to editing the client side of RSPS and im basically having trouble adding more teleports to Trisidia V3's custom teleport interface. For those of you who don't know what the interface looks like I will attach a picture. Basically, under the "islands" tele I want to add more teleports. From my understanding this is all done from the client's side (besides tele cords?). Please excuse my newbieness.
